The platform performed well technically but required more custom development for luxury-specific features. Clienteling integrations that took 2 hours on Shopify Plus took 2 weeks on BigCommerce. The app ecosystem gap is real.

Where BigCommerce won: their headless implementation with a custom Nuxt.js frontend delivered page load times under 1.2 seconds. For luxury brands where bounce rates directly correlate to conversion, that speed advantage justified the additional development investment.

