<h2 id="who-its-for">🎯 Who Each Platform Is For</h2>

<h3>Choose Shopify Plus If You:</h3>

- Operate 3+ retail locations needing unified inventory
- Prioritize omnichannel customer experience
- Need luxury-specific integrations (clienteling, endless aisle, personalization)
- Run exclusive product drops requiring Launchpad functionality
- Want white-glove support during high-stakes launches
- Process under $15 million annually online

Shopify Plus is the default choice for luxury brands prioritizing customer experience across channels. The ecosystem advantage compounds over time as you add locations and complexity.

<h3>Choose BigCommerce Enterprise If You:</h3>

- Have significant wholesale/B2B revenue (40%+ of total)
- Process $15 million+ annually (cost savings become material)
- Want headless architecture for unique brand experiences
- Have strong development resources in-house
- Operate fewer physical locations (under 5)
- Need maximum checkout customization flexibility

BigCommerce Enterprise suits luxury brands with complex B2B needs or those with development teams capable of building custom solutions. The platform provides more control at lower cost, but requires more investment to reach feature parity on luxury-specific capabilities.

