<h2 id="migration-considerations">🔄 Migration Considerations</h2>

If you're currently on another platform, migration complexity varies significantly.

Moving to Shopify Plus typically takes 8-16 weeks for luxury brands. The platform offers migration tools and certified partners who've handled luxury-specific requirements. Budget $25,000-75,000 for a proper implementation including theme customization, app configuration, and data migration.

BigCommerce Enterprise migrations run similarly, though finding partners with luxury retail experience is harder. The platform itself handles data migration well, but the custom development for luxury features extends timelines.

Both platforms can import from major e-commerce systems. The complexity lies in recreating the experience, not moving the data.

